        div We may use the information we collect from you when you register, claim your business, subscribe, respond to a survey or marketing communication, surf the website, or use certain
            b  other site features in the following ways:

        br

        ul.circle
            li To personalize your experience and to allow us to deliver the type of content and product offerings in which you are most interested.
            li To improve our website in order to better serve you.
            li To allow us to better service you in responding to your customer service requests.
            li To administer a contest, promotion, survey or other site feature.
            li To supply feedback to third party businesses.
            li To ask for ratings and reviews of services or products.
            li To follow up with them after correspondence (live chat, email or phone inquiries)
            li To show publicly your commerce, advertising, account profile to the audience to find easily your business (services or products) and you can change the information of account or advertising. you can report us to remove if you believe that somebody creates an unauthorized fake account with your likeness or your identity.
