        br
        ul.circle
            li We may share information about you with third parties, such as advertising identifiers, location data, common account identifier (like an email address), except for payment information, to facilitate the show of targeted advertising. That is so better to read our privacy policies, terms of use, and other policies of all websites and the third party that connected to us. Maybe these suppliers contact you as necessary to take additional information about you to facilitate your requirements.
            li We may share with the third party who provide services or functions on our behalf, including customer service, marketing, business analytics, payment processing, public relations, distribution of surveys, hosting services, network security, technical and tracking and reporting functions and other functions, so that they can do their services or complete your requests or to simplify the delivery of online advertisement appropriate to your interests. Third-party vendors according to their privacy policy share your information.
            li We may share summation information with third parties, like as the number of users that have been exposed to, or clicked on, advertisements with the advertisers and content distributors.
            li You can share or sign up with third party social media websites and services through our site (such as Facebook, Twitter, Google+, ...). When you do so, you are sharing information with those sites, and the information you share will be related to their privacy policies. Note that you can modify your privacy settings with those third-party social media websites.
